bed_coord_counter.py
-p  path to project path containing bed files

Usage: Supply the path to a folder with bed files and this script will do the following:
  1: Determine the largest coord size
  2: For every bed file will count the 5' coord position across position 1 - largest coord size
  3: Produce a matrix for all files within that project folder
Note: This is mainly usefull if you are mapping against 1 sequence (IVT products or consensus sequences for example)


